  &lt;div role=&quot;tabpanel&quot; id=&quot;panel3-returns&quot; aria-labelledby=&quot;tab3-returns&quot; hidden&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;Free returns within 30 days. Print your return label from the returns portal and drop off at any post office.&lt;/p&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
